------------------------------------------------------------------------
Flash Puzzle Game Source Code
------------------------------------------------------------------------

How to build

$ make

Flex SDK 3.0 or later is necessary.
Please prepare the following mp3 files.

bgm01.mp3   Stage BGM1
bgm02.mp3   Stage BGM2
bgm03.mp3   Stage BGM3
bgm04.mp3   BGM for Ending
sound01.mp3 Sound (Falling Stone)
sound02.mp3 Sound (Digging)
sound03.mp3 Sound (Stage Clear)
sound04.mp3 Sound (Falling Player)

If you do not want to prepare the above files,
please try anahori-nosound project.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
You can play this game at

https://sites.google.com/site/kaityoapocalypse/flash/anahori
------------------------------------------------------------------------

